           SHORT="A pre-processor for pmx"
cat << EOF

M-Tx is a preprocessor for PMX that facilitates inputting lyrics. It builds the
PMX input file based on a language very similar to PMX. M-Tx includes most of
PMX's functionality, but it also permits in-line PMX commands to give access to
virtually all of PMX.

EOF
